column5: There is an Outdoor Show on at the Evinrude Center this coming w/e. Its not a big one,but, I wondered if anyone will be going?
Will there be any Mercs there Jack?
Merc's and Yammies, perch on the back of Lunds.  They are'nt too particular. Dwarfie !
I think I'll get there on Sunday for a visit.  Mike
Jeff and I were planning to wander through at some point or other.  If anyone's thinking G2G, we'll happily adjust our schedule to fit in.
I was gonna go on Sat, but can still go Sun instead. I'll be there around 11:ooam.
